00:13:32.510 --> 00:13:37.650
Because you put a ton of fish in
a small area of the open ocean.

00:13:37.650 --> 00:13:40.040
You put a pen there--
a net, basically--

00:13:40.040 --> 00:13:41.960
throw in a bunch of
baby fish, and then you

00:13:41.960 --> 00:13:42.560
start to grow them.

00:13:42.560 --> 00:13:44.169
But you put a ton
of them in there.

00:13:44.169 --> 00:13:45.960
